title: (Weds Full) Bobby’s Napping Challenge for Lunchbox + The Ratings are in for Week 2 of Snake in the Grass + Songs Gaining Popularity Because of TV and Movies
itunes:title: (Weds Full) Bobby’s Napping Challenge for Lunchbox + The Ratings are in for Week 2 of Snake in the Grass + Songs Gaining Popularity Because of TV and Movies
description:
Bobby gives Lunchbox a challenge to nap inside a store for 15 minutes…and what he can win if he pulls it off. Bobby gives details on the ratings for week 2 of Snake in the Grass. Bobby shares a list of 10 songs that became popular after they were featured in movies or tv…some of these you may not even realize came long before!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
